WEBVTT

00:03:28.848 --> 00:03:31.935
She pitched an ad campaign
to Sir Richard himself.

00:03:32.292 --> 00:03:33.959
And it was a huge success.

00:03:34.332 --> 00:03:36.146
SRO: I just thought, "This is amazing.

00:03:36.170 --> 00:03:38.716
I can do no wrong.
My career is just off to the races.

00:03:38.740 --> 00:03:39.891
How awesome is this?"

00:03:39.915 --> 00:03:42.117
AG: That campaign led to a big promotion

00:03:42.141 --> 00:03:45.243
to lead marketing for Virgin's
music division in LA.

00:03:45.633 --> 00:03:50.188
SRO: So I take the job,
thinking that I am the shit at this point.

00:03:50.212 --> 00:03:52.781
You know, I sort of storm in
through the door

00:03:52.805 --> 00:03:55.170
like, "I've been hanging out
with Richard Branson,

00:03:55.194 --> 00:03:57.350
here I am, this is going to be amazing."

00:03:57.834 --> 00:04:00.831
And a year into it,
almost a year to the day,